run_kiss_icp.py is the main file, in this file:
INPUT: 
    Change the path name to the correct path
    [Optional]: Change kiss ICP parameters by setting "CUSTOM_PARAMETERS"= True and changing the parametes
        Normally the settings should be fine
OUTPUT:
    Figures of the results
    Results can be found in KISS ICP results in npy format
 

visualise_kiss_icp_output.py is a extra file to visualise a previous result
INPUT:
    Change RUN_NAME into the name of results file that you want visualised

OUTPUT:
    Figures of the results
    